Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.10,0:00:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the biggest scandal in the\Nhistory of the Czech police.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.40,0:00:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Regrettably, the three people who were killed
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.90,0:00:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,had been involved with the former\NCzechoslovakian secret police.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.61,0:00:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,With this case, I believe that the dark tendencies\Nin the Prague police have all been wiped clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.04,0:00:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen, you are all proud members\Nof the Prague police force.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.58,0:00:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm expecting your actions to reflect the\Nembarrassment you feel in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.42,0:00:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, as the new Chief of Police,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.13,0:00:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to make some big changes in\Norder to gain back the people's trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.05,0:00:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to introduce the special five-member senior\Ninvestigation team sent from the central office.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.06,0:00:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to cooperate with them so that this\Nhorrible incident can finally be resolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.69,0:00:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Detective Suk, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.57,0:00:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.95,0:00:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to express my deep gratitude to you as the\Nnew Chief of Police for your investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.45,0:01:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.04,0:01:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's the case you're in charge of now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.75,0:01:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the case about the caretaker of an unlicensed orphanage that Inspector Zeman was investigating,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.17,0:01:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the Petrov murder case.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.34,0:01:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Please continue your investigation and finish it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.84,0:01:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir. Well, if you'll excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.85,0:01:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.31,0:01:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The tall man that is suspected of killing Inspector Zeman...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.19,0:01:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know anything about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.19,0:01:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I haven't found out anything about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.45,0:01:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. You may leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.29,0:01:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.92,0:01:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Jan Suk.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.55,0:01:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been assigned here for one year.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.22,0:02:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He had a close relationship with Inspector Zeman.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.14,0:02:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He exposed the hidden past of\Ndetectives Patera and Janacek.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.39,0:02:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He had a meeting with Chief Hamlik just before his death.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.19,0:02:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mark that man!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.86,0:02:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.62,0:03:55.59,Monster-Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(750,0)\pos(360,340)}\NThe Monster's Afterimage
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.63,0:04:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.64,0:04:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I was very pleased to actually reach you by\Nphone at the place you said you'd be at.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.77,0:04:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you think you'd been betrayed again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.94,0:04:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.82,0:04:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Orange juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Grimmer, are you sure it's okay\Nto be in such a crowded place?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.79,0:04:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The new Chief of Police hasn't taken you off the\Nsuspect list for the murder of Inspector Zeman,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.59,0:04:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and the former Czechoslovakian secret police must be after you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.01,0:04:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Or could it be that being in crowded places is actually safer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.56,0:04:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no safe places.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.81,0:04:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:05:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If they want to get me, they could do\Nit wherever or whenever they want.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.31,0:05:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,For instance, they could do it from the\Nwindow with the red curtain up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.91,0:05:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Grimmer, who exactly are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.25,0:05:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No way. Why do you have to go through so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.63,0:05:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I just step into things a little too deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.38,0:05:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's nothing to laugh at.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They're coming to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.39,0:05:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.27,0:05:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I step that deep because I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.65,0:05:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Suk is currently at a cafe in the Republic Square.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.61,0:05:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.20,0:05:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That man he's with is definitely Grimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:05:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.41,0:06:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I continue following them for a little longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.67,0:06:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So you were collecting data on\Nthe brainwashing experiments
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.67,0:06:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,that Petrov was performing on children in former East\NGermany, and that's how you got involved in all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.97,0:06:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.34,0:06:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And right before Petrov died, he gave you\Nthe key to a bank safe deposit box?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.14,0:06:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.44,0:06:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He said something about "The Upbringing of a Monster."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.23,0:06:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Upbringing of a Monster?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.02,0:06:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what that means, but it\Nseems that a lot of people want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.32,0:06:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean the former secret police?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.53,0:06:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And a blonde woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.12,0:06:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The children at the nursery home also said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.66,0:06:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Just after Petrov was killed, they saw a pretty\Nblonde woman outside the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.84,0:06:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a clue who that could be?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.06,0:07:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have the faintest idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.69,0:07:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.99,0:07:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be hiding the fact that you're meeting\Nwith me from your higher-ups.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.74,0:07:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay betraying the police like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not hiding anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.54,0:07:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is part of my investigatory discretion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.08,0:07:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,After I'm done investigating, I'll give\Na full report to my superiors.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.55,0:07:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If I search hard enough, I'm sure\NI can prove your innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.68,0:07:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.10,0:07:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look now, but to your left...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.93,0:07:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a man under a parasol reading a newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He seems suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.61,0:07:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The secret police?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.12,0:07:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.91,0:08:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then. Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.87,0:08:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Go where?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.00,0:08:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you bring it? The key I gave\Nyou to the bank safe deposit box.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.96,0:08:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to know the true nature of a monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.05,0:08:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.59,0:08:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's go do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.52,0:08:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Although we might be better off never knowing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.02,0:08:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Haha! You look pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.66,0:08:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That woman is close.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.25,0:08:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.17,0:08:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It must have been my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.09,0:09:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Suk is on the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll follow him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.33,0:09:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I called you earlier. I'm Suk from the Prague police.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.63,0:09:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to have kept you waiting.\NIt's right here. Please go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Here are the safe deposit boxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.66,0:10:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You can verify the contents in the room over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.37,0:10:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,A data report and a cassette tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:10:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a tape recorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.01,0:11:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready? I'm going to play it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.48,0:11:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,511 Kinderheim.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.90,0:11:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A child's voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.24,0:11:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.74,0:11:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.48,0:11:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.61,0:11:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your last name?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.61,0:11:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ask you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.40,0:11:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your last name?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.07,0:11:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Otto.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.08,0:12:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Hans.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.46,0:12:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Thomas.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.59,0:12:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.42,0:12:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one is your real name?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.97,0:12:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,A long, long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.01,0:12:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,In a land far away, there was a monster without a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.39,0:12:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The monster wanted a name so badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.73,0:12:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that some kind of story?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.90,0:12:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I was waiting for Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.69,0:12:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is Anna?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.53,0:12:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I was waiting for Anna... while I\Nwas reading that picture book.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.54,0:12:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This boy is being questioned under the influence of drugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.29,0:12:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.42,0:12:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.04,0:12:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.92,0:12:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I think she's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.26,0:12:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You are quite an exceptional boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.97,0:12:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you afraid of anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.26,0:13:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the thing that frightens you the most?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.69,0:13:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ask a different question.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.94,0:13:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever killed a person?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.15,0:13:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.57,0:13:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Many people died.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.99,0:13:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So many that it seemed like Anna and I\Nwere the only two people in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.41,0:13:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Where was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.37,0:13:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go back to the other question.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.04,0:13:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the thing that frightens you the most?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.34,0:13:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The monster inside of me is getting larger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.47,0:13:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,"Crunch Crunch! Munch Munch! Chomp Chomp! Gulp!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.68,0:13:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,"Crunch Crunch! Munch Munch! Chomp Chomp! Gulp!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.23,0:13:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,"Crunch Crunch! Munch Munch! Chomp Chomp! Gulp!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.11,0:13:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the thing that frightens me the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.19,0:13:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.70,0:14:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.50,0:14:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm going to throw up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.67,0:14:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Mr. Grimmer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.05,0:14:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.09,0:14:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What is on this tape?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.68,0:14:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this "a monster's true nature?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.64,0:14:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.18,0:14:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we don't know what it means...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.65,0:14:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,there are plenty of people who want to get a hold of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.65,0:14:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The former Czechoslovakian secret police...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.28,0:14:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same if you listen to just the beginning\Nor if you listen all the way through.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.66,0:14:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.63,0:14:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do with that tape and report?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.97,0:15:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.22,0:15:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally, it'd be better to store the evidence here, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.02,0:15:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,but you're going to hold on to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.39,0:15:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's leave separately.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.69,0:15:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one they're probably marking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.65,0:15:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me your cellphone number and your address.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.49,0:15:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If we both make it out safe, we can\Nget in contact with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.12,0:16:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I made it home safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.26,0:16:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What a bad feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.02,0:16:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't seem very reliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.98,0:16:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So? A flat on Lanover St, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.74,0:16:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.70,0:16:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We're the ones asking the questions here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.41,0:16:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You know about us, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.50,0:16:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're from that special senior team that\Nwas sent from the central office.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.63,0:17:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Detective Third Rank Novak,\Nand I am Detective Third Rank Zander.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.09,0:17:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you in my apartment?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.30,0:17:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,How long have you been meeting with Grimmer?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.55,0:17:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell us you haven't been.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.76,0:17:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You met him at the cafe in the Republic Square\Nthen headed toward the Prochazka Bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.81,0:17:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know the man in this photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.86,0:17:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Karl Ranke.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.90,0:17:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a big-shot in the former Czechoslovakian\Nsecret police who's gone underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.53,0:17:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't know that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.03,0:17:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We looked into your bank account.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.20,0:17:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a large deposit this month. What was it for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.92,0:17:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.67,0:17:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.13,0:17:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything about that money.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.80,0:17:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother is currently seriously ill at the\NKrumlov National Hospital, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.51,0:17:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It must take a lot of money to pay\Nfor a hospitalization like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.44,0:17:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.98,0:18:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,After your mother divorced your\Nfather, she raised you by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.28,0:18:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You also think very well of your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.66,0:18:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.66,0:18:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd like to search your apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.67,0:18:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Do what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.42,0:18:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have anything to hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.26,0:18:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Do what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.33,0:18:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Zander, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.27,0:19:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.35,0:19:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They were in your washstand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.69,0:19:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen these things before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.82,0:19:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.69,0:19:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't tell if there's a drug in it until we test it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.16,0:19:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The muscle relaxant found in the dead bodies...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.21,0:19:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,was inside whiskey bon-bons.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.42,0:19:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to the station for a little talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.01,0:19:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine. Investigate as thoroughly as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.22,0:19:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.73,0:20:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but could I change my shirt before we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.90,0:20:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.61,0:20:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down. Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.03,0:20:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't do anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.41,0:20:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If I explain it to them, they'll understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.76,0:20:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I smell gun powder?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.80,0:21:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Suk!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.75,0:22:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes... Gazing at what is known now in this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.10,0:23:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes... Your eyes believe in kindness...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.44,0:23:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Make it home... to your land of harmony...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.88,0:23:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Make it home... to your land of purity...
